snippet.title: Terraforming with FeedbackGaming | Surviving Mars: Green Planet Tutorial Part 1
snippet.description:
FeedBackGaming shows off the new Terraforming features of Surviving Mars: Green Planet, which allows you to turn the red wastes of Mars into a Green Planet, and a new home for the human race
Read the first Dev Diary on Terraforming here: https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/index.php?forums/surviving-mars.983/

Be sure to subscribe to our channel for more Green Planet tutorials, and you can also subscribe to FeedBackGaming here! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh8GAqXvXDgQPJxvwTWoXug
